data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, one-bath home that combines modern comfort with classic appeal. This recently updated residence boasts a two-year-old roof, brand-new AC, and water heater, ensuring worry-free living for years to come. The interior features a spacious and inviting atmosphere, with ample natural light illuminating the tastefully designed living spaces. The kitchen is a chef's delight, offering the perfect blend of style and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home – schedule a showing today and experience the best in modern living!    Call a local agent today
